Third-party code bundled with wsmr
===================================

wsmr embeds and ships two POSIX shell helpers adapted from uwsm (Universal
Wayland Session Manager):

  - libexec/prepare-env.sh     (adapted from uwsm/uwsm-libexec/prepare-env.sh)
  - libexec/signal-handler.sh  (adapted from uwsm/uwsm-libexec/signal-handler.sh)

These are compiled into the wsmr binary (include_str!) and extracted at runtime.
Both projects are MIT-licensed, so the only obligation is to preserve the
upstream copyright and license notice, reproduced verbatim below.

Upstream: uwsm — https://github.com/Vladimir-csp/uwsm

